OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes as
OL,4,Cwildfire spreads across island
OL,6,FA gorse wildfire has spread across
OL,7,FLittle Sark, and is thought to be the
OL,8,FIsland's largest ever.
OL,10,FSark Fire and Rescue Service has
OL,11,Frequested assistance from its
OL,12,Fcolleagues in Guernsey, who have sent
OL,13,Fnine firefighters to support
OL,14,Foperations.
OL,16,FITV News understands that up to 4000
OL,17,Fsquare meters of scrubland are alight.
OL,19,FLocal people tell ITV Channel that
OL,20,Fthey have been evacuated from nearby
OL,21,Fhomes and gathered in a "common area".
