OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes as
OL,4,Cwildfire spreads across island
OL,6,FOne resident says it is "all hands on
OL,7,Fdeck" and that the public is helping
OL,8,Fthe fire brigade with "buckets of
OL,9,Fwater and sandwiches".
OL,11,FThe fire is believed to be moving
OL,12,Ftowards the coast because of the
OL,13,Fcurrent wind direction.
OL,15,FSark is the smallest self-governing
OL,16,FChannel Island, around seven miles
OL,17,Feast of Guernsey.
