OL,3,CResidents evacuated from homes as
OL,4,Cwildfire spreads across island
OL,6,FIt has a permanent population of
OL,7,Faround 500 people, which can double
OL,8,Fduring the tourist season with
OL,9,Fvisitors and seasonal staff.
OL,11,FLittle Sark is a small peninsula on
OL,12,Fthe southern side of the island - they
OL,13,Fare joined together by a narrow ridge
OL,14,Fcalled La Coupee.
OL,16,FThis is a developing news story which
OL,17,Fwill be updated.
